caption.title: Histogram of the number of peaks found in the infection time course over 1000 runs of the case of weak population immune strength.
caption.p: The parameters are those used in Fig 3. Peaks were found using FindPeaks, a Mathematica utility, after being smoothed by Wiener filtering. More than three-quarters of the samples have more than one peak in this case in contrast to the strongly immune case shown in S3 Fig.
